@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lwplok(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v1 + 0.19 * v0 + 0.62)))
    tmp = wp.cos((v0 - v1))
    v2 = (tmp * 0.64)
    v0 = (0.15 * ((tmp + 0.12 + v2 + 0.14) * v2))
    tmp = v1
    v0 = (v2 + ((v0 + 0.75 / v2 + 0.17) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.84)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((v0 + 0.70 + v1 + 0.10) + (v0 + 0.77 / tmp + 0.96)))
    data[tid] = v0
